<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Glass Boat</title>
    <style>
        .back{
            font-size: 27px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: black;
        }
        .paragraph{
            font-size: 25px;
        }
        .back:hover{
            color: rgb(37, 37, 37);
        }
        .translation-btn-usa{
            position: absolute;
            height: 50px;
            width: 50px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            cursor: pointer;
            margin-top: -80px;
            margin-left: 1300px;
        }
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .paragraph{
                font-size: 25px;
                width: 280vw;
            }
        }
        .translation-btn-ro{
            position: absolute;
            height: 50px;
            width: 50px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            cursor: pointer;
            margin-top: -80px;
            margin-left: 1390px;
        }
        .invisible{
            display: none;
            top: -1000000px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <a class="back" href="/sharm-el-sheikh/home">     <p class="back">←</p>    </a>
    <div class="translation">
        <img src="/images/1200px-Flag_of_the_United_States.svg.png" class="translation-btn-usa" id="translation-btn-usa">
        <img src="/images/1200px-Flag_of_Romania.svg.png" class="translation-btn-ro" id="translation-btn-ro">
    </div>
    <h1>Glass Boat</h1>
    <p id="paragraph-ro" class="paragraph">
        Barca cu fund de sticlă oferă celor care nu înoată posibilitatea de a admira fauna Mării Roșii, deoarece va naviga la un magnific recif de corali. Excursia cu barcă cu fund de sticlă se adresează tuturor categoriilor de varsta, pentru ca întreaga familie să poată admira viața subacvatică a Mării Roșii. Prin fund de sticlă puteți vedea cu claritate, filma și fotografia corali, bancuri de pești si alte vietăți marine.
        <br><br>
        Cand:<br>
    </p>
    <p id="paragraph-usa" class="paragraph invisible">
        A fantastic opportunity to explore the beautiful coral reefs beneath the crystal clear waters that Red Sea is famous for in Sharm El Sheikh. All while comfortably above water on a glass-bottomed boat. Look out for beautiful colored fish, turtles, rays and dolphins.        When:<br>
    </p>
</body>
<script>
    const translateBtnUsa = document.getElementById("translation-btn-usa")
    const translateBtnRo = document.getElementById("translation-btn-ro")
    const paragraphUsa = document.getElementById("paragraph-usa")
    const paragraphRo = document.getElementById("paragraph-ro")

    translateBtnUsa.addEventListener("click", ()=>{
        paragraphUsa.classList.remove("invisible")
        paragraphRo.classList.add("invisible")
    })

    translateBtnRo.addEventListener("click", ()=>{
        paragraphUsa.classList.add("invisible")
        paragraphRo.classList.remove("invisible")
    })

</script>
</html>